name: After Hours
description:
After Hours 

The night was late, Tina waiting for Joyo to closed their records stall. She was hungry, she always hungry during this hour... 

This is the first month they opened the stall. Tina and Joyo onced worked at the same place and Tina just resigned last week, because of her annoying boss. She refused to take responsiblity because of an error she didn't do. 

Stand up for the truth, that's how she raised. Raised by a single mother, a tough one, a Virgo mom. While Tina was a very stubborn kid back then, as she grew older she tried to be flexible, but she didn't think she managed this time, can't comporimised the blame. Short story, the situation was ugly, she quited the game, at least for now.. 

This time she decided to be the main character, to follow her dreams to owned a record store or a book shop, a new page she would love to write about, doesn't matter how this going to last, baby steps for a long way run, she kept that in mind, no turning back. 

It's getting late and colder, she listens to her favorite playlist while waiting for Joyo to get back from the mini market, she can't wait to eat those warm soupy cup noodles.
___
00:17 secs animated drawings with mixed soundcape audio.
